1
00:00:11,205 --> 00:00:12,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Then buy some nail clippers.</i></font>

2
00:00:12,839 --> 00:00:13,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I've got some.</font>

3
00:00:13,772 --> 00:00:15,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I mean expensive clippers
of your very own.</font>

4
00:00:15,939 --> 00:00:17,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But those are really nice.</font>

5
00:00:17,972 --> 00:00:19,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'd rather use a nice--</font>

6
00:00:19,105 --> 00:00:21,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?
You're staring off into space.</font>

7
00:00:22,305 --> 00:00:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You haven't eaten anything.</font>

8
00:00:25,905 --> 00:00:28,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you were making your own lunch.
Are you already sick of it?</font>

9
00:00:28,839 --> 00:00:31,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I overslept today.</font>

10
00:00:32,939 --> 00:00:35,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, sorry. What were you talking about?</font>

11
00:00:35,472 --> 00:00:37,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was telling you about this.</font>

12
00:00:37,872 --> 00:00:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It says, "This Christmas is the best time
in your life for having a romance.</font>

13
00:00:41,605 --> 00:00:44,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There is an excellent chance
that whoever you spend Christmas Eve with</font>

14
00:00:44,672 --> 00:00:46,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">will be your partner for life."</font>

15
00:00:47,405 --> 00:00:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh...</font>

16
00:00:51,505 --> 00:00:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm really happy for you, Marina.</font>

17
00:00:52,905 --> 00:00:55,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's not me. It's you, Nao.</font>

18
00:00:55,805 --> 00:00:56,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

19
00:00:57,072 --> 00:00:59,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Haven't you made any progress
with Uehara?</font>

20
00:00:59,872 --> 00:01:02,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Christmas Eve's in two weeks.</font>

21
00:01:03,905 --> 00:01:05,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">These horoscopes are never right.</font>

22
00:01:05,939 --> 00:01:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't tell me again this year,</font>

23
00:01:08,505 --> 00:01:11,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I'm going to have a family party
at Daichi's house!"</font>

24
00:01:11,972 --> 00:01:14,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A family party?
You mean your families get together?</font>

25
00:01:14,205 --> 00:01:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, exactly!</font>

26
00:01:17,405 --> 00:01:20,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Without fail,
ever since she was seven years old</font>

27
00:01:20,505 --> 00:01:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">their families gather
around a Christmas cake,</font>

28
00:01:23,305 --> 00:01:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">wear Santa hats, sing "Jingle Bells",</font>

29
00:01:25,572 --> 00:01:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-and exchange presents.
-Unbelievable!</font>

30
00:01:28,839 --> 00:01:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't it?</font>

31
00:01:29,972 --> 00:01:33,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Since your parents aren't here this year,
you can finally get away from Daichi!</font>

32
00:01:33,605 --> 00:01:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then you can make Uehara yours!</font>

33
00:01:36,205 --> 00:01:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told you before,
I'm not interested in Uehara.</font>

34
00:01:39,505 --> 00:01:42,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Speak of the devil.
-Uehara?</font>

35
00:01:43,472 --> 00:01:44,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

36
00:01:46,305 --> 00:01:47,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

37
00:01:51,672 --> 00:01:53,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, that one.</font>

38
00:01:53,205 --> 00:01:54,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What's up?
-Here.</font>

39
00:01:54,839 --> 00:01:56,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's the TV drama you said you missed.</font>

40
00:01:56,939 --> 00:02:00,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, you remembered.</font>

41
00:02:00,405 --> 00:02:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Argh! This is so frustrating.</font>

42
00:02:02,305 --> 00:02:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, until she accepts
her own feelings for Uehara,</font>

43
00:02:05,772 --> 00:02:07,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">it's never going to go anywhere.</font>

44
00:02:12,105 --> 00:02:13,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara! What a stud!</font>

45
00:02:13,772 --> 00:02:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Over here, Uehara! Look this way!</font>

46
00:02:20,405 --> 00:02:21,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>He's so handsome.</i></font>

47
00:02:54,605 --> 00:02:56,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Good morning.</font>

48
00:03:03,405 --> 00:03:06,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I guess he was up all night
at his part-time job again.</font>

49
00:03:31,205 --> 00:03:32,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

50
00:03:34,939 --> 00:03:39,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes? What... is it?</font>

51
00:03:41,672 --> 00:03:42,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your nose hair's sticking out.</font>

52
00:03:44,572 --> 00:03:45,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? Eek!</font>

53
00:03:46,705 --> 00:03:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow. My back hurts.</font>

54
00:03:50,972 --> 00:03:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I was just going to wash my face.</font>

55
00:03:53,105 --> 00:03:56,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It's past noon, you know.
-So what?</font>

56
00:03:56,105 --> 00:03:57,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Today's a holiday.</font>

57
00:03:57,905 --> 00:03:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a slacker.</font>

58
00:03:59,505 --> 00:04:02,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, aren't you going out today?</font>

59
00:04:02,505 --> 00:04:05,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just got back from working
at the gas station,</font>

60
00:04:06,205 --> 00:04:08,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and the cafe's closed today.</font>

61
00:04:08,905 --> 00:04:12,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh? That means...</font>

62
00:04:13,605 --> 00:04:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">today, Uehara and I are...
alone together?</font>

63
00:04:21,039 --> 00:04:22,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

64
00:04:22,105 --> 00:04:24,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So what? It's no big deal.</font>

65
00:04:37,505 --> 00:04:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you doing?</font>

66
00:04:39,505 --> 00:04:41,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you think?
I'm taking a shower.</font>

67
00:04:41,605 --> 00:04:44,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm in here now.</font>

68
00:04:44,072 --> 00:04:46,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Then shut your eyes for a second.
-What?</font>

69
00:04:46,505 --> 00:04:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Stop! Stop that!</font>

70
00:04:52,939 --> 00:04:54,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm coming.</font>

71
00:04:55,305 --> 00:04:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, Yuri--
-Excuse me.</font>

72
00:04:57,405 --> 00:04:59,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry to barge in.</font>

73
00:04:59,105 --> 00:05:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yuri, what's with all the bags?</font>

74
00:05:00,605 --> 00:05:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry, but let me leave these here
for a bit.</font>

75
00:05:03,405 --> 00:05:06,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's a sale going on near here,
so I couldn't help buying all this.</font>

76
00:05:07,472 --> 00:05:08,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ta-da!</font>

77
00:05:08,905 --> 00:05:09,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What do you think?</font>

78
00:05:10,005 --> 00:05:12,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I bought this
for all the year-end parties.</font>

79
00:05:12,905 --> 00:05:14,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's so pretty, Yuri.</font>

80
00:05:14,305 --> 00:05:17,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Nao. You're so sweet.</font>

81
00:05:17,405 --> 00:05:19,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah.
I want to give you some of my clothes.</font>

82
00:05:19,605 --> 00:05:20,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Really?</font>

83
00:05:20,572 --> 00:05:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You spend way too much on clothes.</font>

84
00:05:22,472 --> 00:05:24,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So what if I do.
I earned it myself.</font>

85
00:05:24,905 --> 00:05:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can use it as I please.</font>

86
00:05:26,205 --> 00:05:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't talk to me like that.
I'm letting you leave your bags here.</font>

87
00:05:29,205 --> 00:05:31,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I bought you something too.</font>

88
00:05:32,305 --> 00:05:35,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you think I'm a child
that can be pleased with--</font>

89
00:05:37,605 --> 00:05:39,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THE ORIGINAL <i>TAIYAKI
MEDETAIYA</i></font>

90
00:05:39,972 --> 00:05:40,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh my god!</font>

91
00:05:42,105 --> 00:05:44,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's one of the top three <i>taiyaki shops,
Medetaiya.</i></font>

92
00:05:45,072 --> 00:05:47,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Waiting in line for this wasn't easy.</font>

93
00:05:47,105 --> 00:05:48,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whoa!</font>

94
00:05:48,205 --> 00:05:50,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Before you get this, say you're sorry.</font>

95
00:05:51,005 --> 00:05:52,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm sorry.
-I can't hear you.</font>

96
00:05:52,805 --> 00:05:54,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm sorry!
-Still can't hear you.</font>

97
00:05:54,939 --> 00:05:56,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said I'm sorry!</font>

98
00:05:56,705 --> 00:05:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Say, "Thank you, Yuri."</font>

99
00:05:58,705 --> 00:06:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

100
00:06:00,405 --> 00:06:03,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Say, "I really appreciate--"
-Quit it. They're getting cold.</font>

101
00:06:03,105 --> 00:06:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, fine.</font>

102
00:06:05,505 --> 00:06:07,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Nao, do you want one?</font>

103
00:06:08,472 --> 00:06:11,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I'm going to go
buy something to drink.</font>

104
00:06:33,072 --> 00:06:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Watch out!</font>

105
00:06:46,305 --> 00:06:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

106
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you all right?</font>

107
00:06:52,505 --> 00:06:54,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I'm sorry.
-It hurts.</font>

108
00:07:01,105 --> 00:07:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh...</font>

109
00:07:04,705 --> 00:07:05,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No!</font>

110
00:07:06,039 --> 00:07:07,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">EVENING STAR RAMEN</font>

111
00:07:07,105 --> 00:07:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>$12,000!</i></font>

112
00:07:09,005 --> 00:07:12,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right. A loyal customer
specially asked a famous potter</font>

113
00:07:12,205 --> 00:07:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">to make these bowls.</font>

114
00:07:15,405 --> 00:07:19,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Three bowls cost $12,000.
How are you going to pay for these?</font>

115
00:07:19,105 --> 00:07:20,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're kidding!</font>

116
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:25,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no point in trying
to get it from a high school kid.</font>

117
00:07:25,405 --> 00:07:27,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll talk to your parents
and get it from them.</font>

118
00:07:27,872 --> 00:07:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's your parent's number?</font>

119
00:07:30,205 --> 00:07:32,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-No, you can't.
-What?</font>

120
00:07:32,872 --> 00:07:36,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Because of certain circumstances,
I'm not living with my parents now.</font>

121
00:07:36,939 --> 00:07:38,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

122
00:07:38,205 --> 00:07:42,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If they found out about this,
they'd take me to the countryside.</font>

123
00:07:42,105 --> 00:07:43,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I couldn't care less.</font>

124
00:07:43,872 --> 00:07:46,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Quit expecting special treatment
just because you're a high school kid.</font>

125
00:07:46,772 --> 00:07:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Your problems have got nothing
to do with me.</font>

126
00:07:50,705 --> 00:07:52,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Part-time help wanted,
$9 an hour</font>

127
00:07:53,305 --> 00:07:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Could I pay it off if I worked here?</font>

128
00:07:57,505 --> 00:07:58,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

129
00:07:58,605 --> 00:08:00,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Part-time help wanted,
$9 an hour</font>

130
00:08:01,105 --> 00:08:03,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let me work here, please!</font>

131
00:08:03,505 --> 00:08:04,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you nuts?</font>

132
00:08:04,505 --> 00:08:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll work for the $12,000!</font>

133
00:08:08,072 --> 00:08:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dear Uehara,</font>

134
00:08:11,305 --> 00:08:17,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just remembered something I had to do,
so I won't be coming home until late.</font>

135
00:08:19,039 --> 00:08:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Send.</font>

136
00:08:22,972 --> 00:08:26,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know I promised to do this,
but I'm not sure I can.</font>

137
00:08:29,205 --> 00:08:33,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And these clothes... are hideous.</font>

138
00:08:35,472 --> 00:08:38,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Totally hideous.</font>

139
00:08:40,772 --> 00:08:43,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He said he didn't care
if these got dirty</font>

140
00:08:43,505 --> 00:08:45,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but these are junior high PE clothes.</font>

141
00:08:46,105 --> 00:08:49,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The gap between Yuri
and me is getting even bigger.</font>

142
00:08:50,205 --> 00:08:51,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Eek!</font>

143
00:08:52,605 --> 00:08:54,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What the hell are you doing,
you idiot?</font>

144
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:58,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How many more plates
are you going to break?</font>

145
00:08:58,205 --> 00:08:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

146
00:08:59,205 --> 00:09:00,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">WELCOME! WE'RE OPEN</font>

147
00:09:03,605 --> 00:09:05,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm in so much pain.</font>

148
00:09:08,605 --> 00:09:11,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I never thought it would be so hard.</font>

149
00:09:19,039 --> 00:09:20,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm home.</font>

150
00:09:20,505 --> 00:09:22,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure are late.</font>

151
00:09:22,572 --> 00:09:26,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, sorry.
Huh? Where's Yuri?</font>

152
00:09:26,572 --> 00:09:28,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She left a long time ago.</font>

153
00:09:30,205 --> 00:09:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! No!</font>

154
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:38,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you want some ramen,
one serving is 89 cents.</font>

155
00:09:43,472 --> 00:09:45,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, thank you.</font>

156
00:09:52,205 --> 00:09:54,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where did this tree come from?</font>

157
00:09:54,605 --> 00:09:56,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Yuri gave it to us.</font>

158
00:09:57,105 --> 00:09:58,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a housewarming present.</font>

159
00:09:58,505 --> 00:10:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow.</font>

160
00:10:00,305 --> 00:10:02,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I told her we didn't need it
because it'll get in the way.</font>

161
00:10:05,105 --> 00:10:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>"There is an excellent chance
that whoever you spend Christmas Eve with</i></font>

162
00:10:08,472 --> 00:10:10,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">will be your partner for life."</font>

163
00:10:14,105 --> 00:10:18,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara, you're working on the 24th, right?</font>

164
00:10:19,072 --> 00:10:21,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah. I work all night.</font>

165
00:10:23,572 --> 00:10:25,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I thought so.
-Huh?</font>

166
00:10:26,105 --> 00:10:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why do you ask?</font>

167
00:10:28,472 --> 00:10:29,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No reason.</font>

168
00:10:31,305 --> 00:10:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just thought working
on Christmas Eve must be kind of lonely.</font>

169
00:10:36,205 --> 00:10:37,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's so stupid.</font>

170
00:10:38,105 --> 00:10:40,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's only lonely people
that worry about that kind of thing.</font>

171
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:46,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who said I was worried about it?</font>

172
00:10:46,605 --> 00:10:48,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then why did you ask?</font>

173
00:10:50,205 --> 00:10:53,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... Just forget about it.</font>

174
00:10:57,105 --> 00:10:58,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a weirdo.</font>

175
00:11:00,905 --> 00:11:02,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Damn him!</font>

176
00:11:02,505 --> 00:11:03,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow!</font>

177
00:11:04,205 --> 00:11:06,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That hurts!</font>

178
00:11:07,772 --> 00:11:10,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>So you're working part-time
at a ramen shop to pay it off?</i></font>

179
00:11:10,305 --> 00:11:12,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you spend all your time working</font>

180
00:11:12,505 --> 00:11:14,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you'll make even less progress
with Uehara.</font>

181
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:18,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Christmas Eve is... only ten days away.</font>

182
00:11:18,205 --> 00:11:21,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How many times do I have to tell you?
I've got no feeling for Uehara.</font>

183
00:11:21,939 --> 00:11:25,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-There you go again.
-I'm serious.</font>

184
00:11:25,705 --> 00:11:30,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, he complains about everything
and eats so much that it's frightening.</font>

185
00:11:30,772 --> 00:11:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">When we're together,
he totally looks down on me.</font>

186
00:11:34,472 --> 00:11:37,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And he makes me feel so miserable.</font>

187
00:11:37,839 --> 00:11:40,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In fact, now that I'm working,
we won't have to see each other.</font>

188
00:11:40,805 --> 00:11:42,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's probably for the better.</font>

189
00:11:53,705 --> 00:11:54,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

190
00:11:55,505 --> 00:12:00,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Will you spend Christmas with me?"</font>

191
00:12:00,072 --> 00:12:03,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Really? Who's it from?
-Marina!</font>

192
00:12:03,105 --> 00:12:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"I'll be waiting for you on the roof
after school."</font>

193
00:12:06,072 --> 00:12:07,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Abe Jun."</font>

194
00:12:07,305 --> 00:12:09,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe Jun. Isn't he in class B?</font>

195
00:12:09,305 --> 00:12:11,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Oh, it's just Abe.
-Huh?</font>

196
00:12:11,905 --> 00:12:13,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's finally gotten around to Nao.</font>

197
00:12:13,872 --> 00:12:15,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Do you know him?</font>

198
00:12:15,305 --> 00:12:16,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

199
00:12:16,839 --> 00:12:17,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

200
00:12:19,105 --> 00:12:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got a great idea.</font>

201
00:12:22,705 --> 00:12:24,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Get over here, Mitsuishi. Come on.
-Nao...</font>

202
00:12:24,505 --> 00:12:26,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. You stay over there.</font>

203
00:12:27,939 --> 00:12:29,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This is to help out Nao.</font>

204
00:12:30,705 --> 00:12:31,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'll tell Uehara...</font>

205
00:12:39,705 --> 00:12:40,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

206
00:12:47,605 --> 00:12:48,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm...</font>

207
00:12:49,205 --> 00:12:52,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like you.
I've always been attracted to you.</font>

208
00:12:52,105 --> 00:12:54,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please spend Christmas Eve with me.</font>

209
00:12:57,672 --> 00:13:01,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uhm, when I see you, Nao,</font>

210
00:13:01,472 --> 00:13:04,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I feel like I want to protect you.
-I feel like I want to protect you.</font>

211
00:13:04,405 --> 00:13:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

212
00:13:06,872 --> 00:13:09,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My friend just told me about you.</font>

213
00:13:10,171 --> 00:13:12,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You always tell the girls the same thing.</font>

214
00:13:13,939 --> 00:13:16,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-<i>The king of the love confession?
-<i>That's right.</i></i></font>

215
00:13:16,405 --> 00:13:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Abe's famous among some of the girls.</font>

216
00:13:19,672 --> 00:13:21,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's always falling in love.</font>

217
00:13:21,505 --> 00:13:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Every girl he falls for, he texts,
then they all turn him down.</font>

218
00:13:25,772 --> 00:13:27,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is he really that unpopular?</font>

219
00:13:27,505 --> 00:13:28,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

220
00:13:28,505 --> 00:13:30,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's not that bad looking.</font>

221
00:13:30,305 --> 00:13:32,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he's not the type you'd want
as a boyfriend.</font>

222
00:13:33,005 --> 00:13:34,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao would never go with a guy like that.</font>

223
00:13:34,905 --> 00:13:38,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But we can use him.
-We can?</font>

224
00:13:39,605 --> 00:13:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh! Uehara!</font>

225
00:13:41,772 --> 00:13:44,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wait! Wait! Uehara!</font>

226
00:13:46,705 --> 00:13:47,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can we talk for a minute?</font>

227
00:13:53,605 --> 00:13:54,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Please.</font>

228
00:13:54,972 --> 00:13:57,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you may not believe me,</font>

229
00:13:57,505 --> 00:14:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I <i>do like you, Nao.</i></font>

230
00:14:04,305 --> 00:14:05,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. I'm sorry.</font>

231
00:14:07,972 --> 00:14:10,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean it's true
that you and Uehara are dating?</font>

232
00:14:10,672 --> 00:14:13,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Uh...</font>

233
00:14:15,205 --> 00:14:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, yes.</font>

234
00:14:18,005 --> 00:14:19,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This world just isn't fair.</font>

235
00:14:20,605 --> 00:14:25,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's handsome, smart and good at sports.</font>

236
00:14:25,305 --> 00:14:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He attracts girls without even trying.</font>

237
00:14:28,105 --> 00:14:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He hasn't got a worry in the world.</font>

238
00:14:32,105 --> 00:14:35,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara has a lot of worries.</font>

239
00:14:36,505 --> 00:14:37,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really? He does?</font>

240
00:14:37,805 --> 00:14:38,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

241
00:14:39,205 --> 00:14:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He's got a couple of jobs
so he can earn living expenses.</font>

242
00:14:43,905 --> 00:14:45,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he doesn't even think</font>

243
00:14:45,805 --> 00:14:48,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that he's got it harder than anyone else.</font>

244
00:14:48,972 --> 00:14:54,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He may look selfish,
but he's always thinking of others.</font>

245
00:14:55,305 --> 00:14:56,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see.</font>

246
00:14:58,105 --> 00:15:01,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm still jealous of Uehara.</font>

247
00:15:01,205 --> 00:15:02,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

248
00:15:02,205 --> 00:15:03,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's nobody I know</font>

249
00:15:03,705 --> 00:15:06,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">who would say things like that about me.</font>

250
00:15:07,972 --> 00:15:10,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, there is. I'm certain there is.</font>

251
00:15:10,705 --> 00:15:12,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One day you'll meet someone</font>

252
00:15:12,472 --> 00:15:14,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">who can't live without you.</font>

253
00:15:16,105 --> 00:15:19,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I'm not that person.</font>

254
00:15:22,405 --> 00:15:23,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm sorry.</font>

255
00:15:26,105 --> 00:15:27,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look.</font>

256
00:15:27,705 --> 00:15:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's the first time in her life
that anyone's told her they like her.</font>

257
00:15:31,472 --> 00:15:33,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But she has no choice
but to turn him down.</font>

258
00:15:33,605 --> 00:15:34,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

259
00:15:34,972 --> 00:15:36,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here at school,</font>

260
00:15:36,405 --> 00:15:39,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">everyone thinks you and she are dating.</font>

261
00:15:39,105 --> 00:15:40,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If she told him OK,</font>

262
00:15:40,605 --> 00:15:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">the rumor would spread
that she was two-timing you.</font>

263
00:15:43,105 --> 00:15:46,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Imagine the punishment she'd get
from your fans.</font>

264
00:15:46,405 --> 00:15:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">And although she tries to spend
Christmas Eve with other friends,</font>

265
00:15:49,305 --> 00:15:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">they wouldn't let her join
since she has a boyfriend.</font>

266
00:15:51,772 --> 00:15:53,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's only doing it
because she's away from her family</font>

267
00:15:53,972 --> 00:15:55,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and she's lonely.</font>

268
00:15:55,705 --> 00:15:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that right, Mitsuishi?</font>

269
00:15:57,705 --> 00:15:58,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.</font>

270
00:15:59,305 --> 00:16:02,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In fact, Marina and I've got
plans for Christmas Eve already.</font>

271
00:16:02,405 --> 00:16:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So we can't spend it with her.</font>

272
00:16:05,672 --> 00:16:08,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know, I'm glad I talked to you, Nao.</font>

273
00:16:08,505 --> 00:16:11,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to work hard
at developing a real relationship.</font>

274
00:16:12,305 --> 00:16:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Good.
-Bye.</font>

275
00:16:19,972 --> 00:16:22,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What a pity.</font>

276
00:16:22,505 --> 00:16:26,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She had to destroy a chance
that she'll never have again.</font>

277
00:16:29,805 --> 00:16:33,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, it would be kind of nice, you know,</font>

278
00:16:33,305 --> 00:16:37,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">if you showed just a little kindness
to Nao.</font>

279
00:16:44,039 --> 00:16:46,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course Christmas Eve is special
for girls.</font>

280
00:16:46,972 --> 00:16:49,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-It is?
-You see, girls just love</font>

281
00:16:49,305 --> 00:16:53,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">dressing up, feeling a thrill,
and experiencing love over and over again.</font>

282
00:16:53,839 --> 00:16:55,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Christmas Eve is all that wrapped
into one.</font>

283
00:16:56,305 --> 00:16:58,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Spending it all alone is like</font>

284
00:16:58,705 --> 00:17:02,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">God telling you that you're a failure
as a woman.</font>

285
00:17:02,505 --> 00:17:04,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's hard to believe you're still
in junior high.</font>

286
00:17:04,872 --> 00:17:05,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So right now</font>

287
00:17:05,905 --> 00:17:09,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">all the girls are in a mad dash
to avoid spending it alone.</font>

288
00:17:09,672 --> 00:17:10,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A mad dash?</font>

289
00:17:10,939 --> 00:17:14,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What I mean is they're going to parties
and looking for a partner.</font>

290
00:17:14,205 --> 00:17:16,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-What?
-Boys are the same, right?</font>

291
00:17:16,839 --> 00:17:20,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Lately, even I've been asked out
by a lot of guys.</font>

292
00:17:20,972 --> 00:17:22,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Could it be...
-But there's already this guy I like.</font>

293
00:17:22,939 --> 00:17:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's why she's been coming home
so late recently?</font>

294
00:17:26,405 --> 00:17:29,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For the time being,
I can only work at night.</font>

295
00:17:30,205 --> 00:17:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But even if I work all day
after winter break starts on the 24th...</font>

296
00:17:41,905 --> 00:17:43,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah...</font>

297
00:17:44,205 --> 00:17:47,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How long will it take
to pay back the $12,000?</font>

298
00:17:52,072 --> 00:17:54,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... I know what to do.</font>

299
00:17:54,872 --> 00:17:56,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Mom.</font>

300
00:17:56,605 --> 00:17:58,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">MOM</font>

301
00:17:58,605 --> 00:18:02,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, no, no...
I've got to deal with this myself.</font>

302
00:18:06,405 --> 00:18:08,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nine dollars an hour...</font>

303
00:18:09,505 --> 00:18:12,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If I work eight hours a day...</font>

304
00:18:14,105 --> 00:18:16,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? That's all I'll make?</font>

305
00:18:18,772 --> 00:18:20,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No!</font>

306
00:18:25,805 --> 00:18:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, dear.</font>

307
00:18:28,972 --> 00:18:30,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What should I do?</font>

308
00:18:30,939 --> 00:18:34,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It'll never happen.
I don't know what to do.</font>

309
00:18:34,605 --> 00:18:37,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ahh... I can't handle this.</font>

310
00:18:38,205 --> 00:18:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Thank you.
-Thank you for coming.</font>

311
00:18:44,072 --> 00:18:46,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Here we are. Here's your miso ramen.</font>

312
00:18:46,972 --> 00:18:50,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's such a pleasure
seeing your smiling face, Nao.</font>

313
00:18:50,205 --> 00:18:52,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, come on. Give me a break.</font>

314
00:18:52,705 --> 00:18:54,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Excuse me. Could I get some water?</font>

315
00:18:54,605 --> 00:18:56,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sure. I'll be there in a second.</font>

316
00:18:56,605 --> 00:18:58,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In spite of everything,
she's fitting right in.</font>

317
00:18:58,905 --> 00:19:00,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why don't you take a quick break, Nao?</font>

318
00:19:01,039 --> 00:19:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

319
00:19:02,505 --> 00:19:05,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just don't feel right not working.</font>

320
00:19:05,605 --> 00:19:08,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean,
I broke seven dishes in three days</font>

321
00:19:08,605 --> 00:19:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and I wasted five bowls of ramen.</font>

322
00:19:10,705 --> 00:19:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's no big deal at all.</font>

323
00:19:13,405 --> 00:19:15,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes, it is a big deal, Dad.</font>

324
00:19:19,939 --> 00:19:21,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Welcome.
-Hi, Nao.</font>

325
00:19:21,939 --> 00:19:23,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Marina. Mitsuishi. You came.</font>

326
00:19:24,039 --> 00:19:25,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Look at you, Nao.</font>

327
00:19:25,839 --> 00:19:27,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's one crazy outfit.</font>

328
00:19:27,705 --> 00:19:29,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But it oddly suits her.</font>

329
00:19:29,839 --> 00:19:30,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

330
00:19:30,872 --> 00:19:33,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I hate to admit it, but I agree.</font>

331
00:19:34,205 --> 00:19:37,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Actually,
we've brought along a special guest.</font>

332
00:19:37,305 --> 00:19:38,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

333
00:19:38,805 --> 00:19:41,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-We really just ran into him outside.
-Don't say that.</font>

334
00:19:43,205 --> 00:19:44,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yo.</font>

335
00:19:45,505 --> 00:19:46,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

336
00:19:47,905 --> 00:19:50,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Let's eat.</font>

337
00:20:06,305 --> 00:20:07,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We're done.</font>

338
00:20:07,705 --> 00:20:09,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was delicious.</font>

339
00:20:09,505 --> 00:20:11,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You've got quite an appetite, miss.</font>

340
00:20:11,305 --> 00:20:14,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, wow! What a nice looking guy!</font>

341
00:20:14,405 --> 00:20:17,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-That's Issei, the bully.
-I see.</font>

342
00:20:17,972 --> 00:20:19,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Call me Icchan.</font>

343
00:20:19,305 --> 00:20:21,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">All the customers do.</font>

344
00:20:21,205 --> 00:20:23,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That was really good, Icchan.</font>

345
00:20:26,605 --> 00:20:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's really hard to believe
Nao's working a part-time job.</font>

346
00:20:30,005 --> 00:20:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She believed in Santa Claus
until she was a sixth grader.</font>

347
00:20:32,205 --> 00:20:33,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Seriously?</font>

348
00:20:33,705 --> 00:20:37,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Every year, my dad dressed up as Santa
for Nao's sake.</font>

349
00:20:37,305 --> 00:20:40,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It wasn't easy for me
to act like I was happy too.</font>

350
00:20:40,171 --> 00:20:43,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You sure have a knack
for making people fret over you.</font>

351
00:20:43,105 --> 00:20:44,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry.</font>

352
00:20:44,105 --> 00:20:46,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It just shows how happy it made us
to see your reaction.</font>

353
00:20:46,705 --> 00:20:49,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She would get all excited
over each little present.</font>

354
00:20:49,072 --> 00:20:51,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.
Ever since I was little,</font>

355
00:20:51,405 --> 00:20:55,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I really looked forward to seeing
what present Daichi would get me.</font>

356
00:20:55,205 --> 00:20:57,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I liked the prize
more than the candy it came with.</font>

357
00:20:57,672 --> 00:21:00,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I liked the picture on the box
more than the game inside.</font>

358
00:21:00,072 --> 00:21:03,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He always knew exactly
what would please me.</font>

359
00:21:03,605 --> 00:21:04,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao!</font>

360
00:21:04,572 --> 00:21:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Yes?
-Quit slacking off.</font>

361
00:21:06,105 --> 00:21:07,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Get going.
-Sorry.</font>

362
00:21:07,672 --> 00:21:09,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Enjoy yourselves.</font>

363
00:21:17,105 --> 00:21:18,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Nao.
-Yes?</font>

364
00:21:18,505 --> 00:21:20,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you don't have any plans
for Christmas Eve,</font>

365
00:21:20,472 --> 00:21:21,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">would you like to spend it together?</font>

366
00:21:22,405 --> 00:21:25,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can get it off
from the ramen shop, right?</font>

367
00:21:25,572 --> 00:21:29,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah.
It is a yearly tradition, after all.</font>

368
00:21:29,505 --> 00:21:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I look forward to your mom's
juicy hamburger steaks.</font>

369
00:21:35,772 --> 00:21:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">This year,
why don't we spend it alone together?</font>

370
00:21:38,305 --> 00:21:39,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

371
00:21:39,472 --> 00:21:40,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The family party is fine,</font>

372
00:21:41,039 --> 00:21:43,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but I thought you'd like
that kind of thing better, Nao.</font>

373
00:21:43,605 --> 00:21:45,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-You don't have--
-Shh!</font>

374
00:21:45,205 --> 00:21:46,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Go!</font>

375
00:21:48,305 --> 00:21:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's wrong?</font>

376
00:21:52,705 --> 00:21:53,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Is that Uehara?</font>

377
00:21:54,705 --> 00:21:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't want him to see me like this.</font>

378
00:21:57,605 --> 00:22:01,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't you dare tell Uehara
that I'm working this job.</font>

379
00:22:01,105 --> 00:22:02,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

380
00:22:07,072 --> 00:22:09,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whew.</font>

381
00:22:09,472 --> 00:22:13,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank goodness. Let's go.</font>

382
00:22:26,205 --> 00:22:28,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow!</font>

383
00:22:30,839 --> 00:22:32,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Nao!</font>

384
00:22:32,305 --> 00:22:34,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How many times have I told you
to pick up your stuff?</font>

385
00:22:41,039 --> 00:22:44,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey... Wake up.</font>

386
00:23:12,472 --> 00:23:13,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm home.</font>

387
00:23:14,039 --> 00:23:16,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hi. Welcome back.</font>

388
00:23:20,839 --> 00:23:21,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You OK?</font>

389
00:23:23,105 --> 00:23:26,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm fine. Just a little tired.</font>

390
00:23:36,505 --> 00:23:37,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What is it?</font>

391
00:23:42,105 --> 00:23:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Such a nice smell.</font>

392
00:23:44,505 --> 00:23:45,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

393
00:23:51,972 --> 00:23:54,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Pork soup base with Japanese broth.</font>

394
00:23:55,605 --> 00:23:56,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ah! Hey!</font>

395
00:23:56,772 --> 00:23:58,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Cut that out.</font>

396
00:23:59,839 --> 00:24:01,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm tired.</font>

397
00:24:02,572 --> 00:24:04,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">First I'll take a bath.</font>

398
00:24:04,305 --> 00:24:06,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, would you like to go somewhere
on the 24th?</font>

399
00:24:07,805 --> 00:24:08,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

400
00:24:10,039 --> 00:24:13,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I got the day off from work.</font>

401
00:24:16,705 --> 00:24:17,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did you hear me?</font>

402
00:24:19,839 --> 00:24:24,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... Yes, I see.</font>

403
00:24:25,105 --> 00:24:27,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK... Where are we going?</font>

404
00:24:27,905 --> 00:24:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Where should we go?</font>

405
00:24:29,205 --> 00:24:31,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... We could have dinner here.</font>

406
00:24:32,205 --> 00:24:38,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then we could see the Christmas lights
and take a walk.</font>

407
00:24:39,005 --> 00:24:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, that's it. That's what we'll do.</font>

408
00:24:44,939 --> 00:24:46,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with her?</font>

409
00:24:49,305 --> 00:24:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes!</font>

410
00:24:52,072 --> 00:24:54,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">"Would you like to go somewhere
on the 24th?</font>

411
00:24:54,905 --> 00:24:57,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I got the day off from work."</font>

412
00:25:01,305 --> 00:25:02,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes! Yes!</font>

413
00:25:03,205 --> 00:25:05,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ow! Ow!</font>

414
00:25:05,472 --> 00:25:08,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Yes! Well done!</i></font>

415
00:25:09,572 --> 00:25:13,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can hardly believe it!
You're spending Christmas Eve</font>

416
00:25:13,105 --> 00:25:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">with our school's pride and joy,
a super-rare, high-class stud.</font>

417
00:25:19,105 --> 00:25:22,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara just happened to get the day off
from work.</font>

418
00:25:22,572 --> 00:25:24,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's all.</font>

419
00:25:24,205 --> 00:25:26,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He just kind of wondered
if I wanted to go somewhere, I think.</font>

420
00:25:27,405 --> 00:25:30,138
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I don't particularly care
if we do or not.</font>

421
00:25:30,205 --> 00:25:32,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, yeah. Whatever, whatever.</font>

422
00:25:32,305 --> 00:25:35,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can finally move on from Daichi, huh?</font>

423
00:25:37,072 --> 00:25:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, no!</font>

424
00:25:39,472 --> 00:25:41,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi is at a training camp
until tomorrow.</font>

425
00:25:42,572 --> 00:25:46,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, I see. Thank you.</font>

426
00:25:47,072 --> 00:25:48,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I think it'll be fine.</font>

427
00:25:48,972 --> 00:25:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi did say,
"If you don't have any plans," right?</font>

428
00:25:51,472 --> 00:25:52,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

429
00:25:52,505 --> 00:25:55,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But he said he wanted to spend it
alone together this year.</font>

430
00:25:55,805 --> 00:25:59,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He just means spending it together
like siblings would, right?</font>

431
00:26:00,005 --> 00:26:02,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean,
Daichi is one of the top three studs.</font>

432
00:26:02,972 --> 00:26:06,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He could easily find someone
to spend Christmas Eve with.</font>

433
00:26:06,905 --> 00:26:10,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">In fact, I'm surprised you've been friends
for ten years.</font>

434
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:16,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Anyway,
I'll keep trying to get hold of him.</font>

435
00:26:18,039 --> 00:26:21,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, wow! I am so happy for you.</font>

436
00:26:21,505 --> 00:26:23,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The day is coming soon</font>

437
00:26:23,105 --> 00:26:27,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">when you won't be faking it anymore,
but you'll really be his girlfriend.</font>

438
00:26:27,105 --> 00:26:29,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I knew it. You're faking it.</font>

439
00:26:30,039 --> 00:26:31,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

440
00:26:32,505 --> 00:26:34,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Whoa, Abe!</font>

441
00:26:34,405 --> 00:26:35,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Where'd you come from?
-Listen.</font>

442
00:26:35,872 --> 00:26:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I haven't been able to get Nao
out of my head.</font>

443
00:26:38,472 --> 00:26:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">My, you're unusually slow
getting over it this time.</font>

444
00:26:40,839 --> 00:26:42,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How could it possibly be true?</font>

445
00:26:43,405 --> 00:26:45,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no way you're dating Uehara.</font>

446
00:26:45,472 --> 00:26:49,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao, I don't know why you're doing it</font>

447
00:26:49,605 --> 00:26:53,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but don't you feel it's meaningless
to fake being Uehara's girlfriend?</font>

448
00:26:53,072 --> 00:26:54,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If so, then I--</font>

449
00:26:54,205 --> 00:26:55,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Aah!</font>

450
00:26:57,005 --> 00:26:58,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Keep quiet, Abe!</font>

451
00:26:58,839 --> 00:27:01,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How about you and I go to a party
on Christmas Eve, OK?</font>

452
00:27:01,505 --> 00:27:03,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There'll be swarms of cute girls there.</font>

453
00:27:03,105 --> 00:27:04,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Well, I'd rather--
-Shut up.</font>

454
00:27:05,039 --> 00:27:06,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Forget her, OK?</font>

455
00:27:16,839 --> 00:27:18,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How pretty.</font>

456
00:27:22,572 --> 00:27:23,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

457
00:27:23,872 --> 00:27:25,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">$390.</font>

458
00:27:25,905 --> 00:27:27,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's so expensive.</font>

459
00:27:33,405 --> 00:27:35,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, Yuri.</font>

460
00:27:36,505 --> 00:27:37,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you up to?</font>

461
00:27:39,605 --> 00:27:41,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Ah...
-Yes?</font>

462
00:27:43,905 --> 00:27:47,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yep, I think this one suits you best.</font>

463
00:27:48,405 --> 00:27:49,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-But--
-Don't you like it?</font>

464
00:27:51,072 --> 00:27:54,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, then this is my Christmas present
to you.</font>

465
00:27:54,839 --> 00:27:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

466
00:27:56,072 --> 00:27:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No, I can't take this--</font>

467
00:27:57,805 --> 00:28:00,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's one of my old ones,
so don't worry about it.</font>

468
00:28:02,105 --> 00:28:04,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sure it's OK?</font>

469
00:28:04,105 --> 00:28:05,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-huh.</font>

470
00:28:19,772 --> 00:28:22,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Now, as for the food, he likes meat.</font>

471
00:28:23,072 --> 00:28:25,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But as for soup, he likes seafood.</font>

472
00:28:26,039 --> 00:28:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He likes any kind of pasta.</font>

473
00:28:28,105 --> 00:28:29,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I see...</font>

474
00:28:29,905 --> 00:28:32,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The soup should be seafood.</font>

475
00:28:32,505 --> 00:28:34,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, got it.</font>

476
00:28:34,872 --> 00:28:37,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... but I'm not really...</font>

477
00:28:38,905 --> 00:28:41,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There's no need to play dumb, Nao.</font>

478
00:28:42,039 --> 00:28:44,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can see you're in love.
It's written all over your face.</font>

479
00:28:44,972 --> 00:28:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But what's the point
in admitting that I am?</font>

480
00:28:48,705 --> 00:28:50,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why do you say that?</font>

481
00:28:50,705 --> 00:28:52,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You know what I'm talking about, Yuri.</font>

482
00:28:52,872 --> 00:28:55,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You told me his heart isn't
so easily moved.</font>

483
00:28:56,672 --> 00:28:58,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's true.</font>

484
00:28:59,205 --> 00:29:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but if he made you his girlfriend</font>

485
00:29:01,005 --> 00:29:03,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that's exactly why he'd treat you
with very special care.</font>

486
00:29:19,972 --> 00:29:21,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hi.</font>

487
00:29:27,305 --> 00:29:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Can you give Nao a message?</font>

488
00:29:32,105 --> 00:29:35,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tell her I'll come get her tomorrow,
Christmas Eve, just past noon.</font>

489
00:29:36,072 --> 00:29:37,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Tomorrow, Christmas Eve?</font>

490
00:29:38,005 --> 00:29:39,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's right.</font>

491
00:29:39,105 --> 00:29:42,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Our families get together every year
on Christmas Eve.</font>

492
00:29:42,205 --> 00:29:44,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But I've decided she and I would
spend it together this year.</font>

493
00:29:47,572 --> 00:29:50,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've decided
that's how it will be from now on.</font>

494
00:29:58,472 --> 00:29:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Later.</font>

495
00:30:21,839 --> 00:30:23,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Welcome home.</font>

496
00:30:23,305 --> 00:30:27,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">So, about tomorrow,
I was thinking of having dinner early.</font>

497
00:30:27,605 --> 00:30:28,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nah, I've got work tomorrow.</font>

498
00:30:29,005 --> 00:30:31,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK, then I'll have it ready
by six o'clock tomor...</font>

499
00:30:32,205 --> 00:30:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

500
00:30:33,305 --> 00:30:34,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

501
00:30:34,805 --> 00:30:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What did you just say?</font>

502
00:30:36,205 --> 00:30:38,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've got work tomorrow.</font>

503
00:30:38,872 --> 00:30:40,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But... Why?</font>

504
00:30:41,005 --> 00:30:43,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You already had something planned, right?</font>

505
00:30:43,872 --> 00:30:47,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You should have told me
you were doing something with that senior.</font>

506
00:30:47,305 --> 00:30:49,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Senior? You mean Daichi?</font>

507
00:30:50,005 --> 00:30:51,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I plan on turning down Daichi--</font>

508
00:30:51,505 --> 00:30:53,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You celebrated with him every year, right?</font>

509
00:30:53,605 --> 00:30:56,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">There is no point for me
to go out of my way</font>

510
00:30:56,205 --> 00:30:57,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">and worry over you.</font>

511
00:30:58,805 --> 00:31:00,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Worry over me?</font>

512
00:31:02,572 --> 00:31:04,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You invited me out
because you were worried about me?</font>

513
00:31:04,905 --> 00:31:09,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">On top of faking like we're dating,
I've caused you other problems too.</font>

514
00:31:10,205 --> 00:31:14,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's that supposed to mean?
What makes you think you're responsible?</font>

515
00:31:14,505 --> 00:31:17,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? Weren't you panicking over it?</font>

516
00:31:18,039 --> 00:31:21,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Along with that girl, Marina,</font>

517
00:31:21,105 --> 00:31:23,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">weren't you looking for a date
for Christmas Eve?</font>

518
00:31:23,772 --> 00:31:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What? No, I wasn't.</font>

519
00:31:29,572 --> 00:31:30,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then...</font>

520
00:31:30,972 --> 00:31:33,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">why have you been coming home
so late recently?</font>

521
00:31:37,505 --> 00:31:38,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well...</font>

522
00:31:41,205 --> 00:31:42,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well what?</font>

523
00:31:45,405 --> 00:31:46,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I had work.</font>

524
00:31:46,505 --> 00:31:48,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Work? Where?</font>

525
00:31:52,839 --> 00:31:55,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">At a cafe... near the station.</font>

526
00:31:55,572 --> 00:31:57,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You look like you're lying.</font>

527
00:31:57,405 --> 00:31:58,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm not.</font>

528
00:32:00,171 --> 00:32:02,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Well, I don't really understand it,</font>

529
00:32:02,605 --> 00:32:04,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">but Christmas Eve is special to girls,
right?</font>

530
00:32:04,839 --> 00:32:07,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You bet it is. It's very special.</font>

531
00:32:08,105 --> 00:32:10,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a day you spend having fun
and eating cake</font>

532
00:32:10,171 --> 00:32:13,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">with the people who are special to you,
whether it's a sweetheart or family.</font>

533
00:32:15,205 --> 00:32:20,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It can't be just anyone.
It matters who you spend it with.</font>

534
00:32:24,205 --> 00:32:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then... it must be nice having him around.</font>

535
00:32:34,205 --> 00:32:36,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, just forget it!</font>

536
00:32:40,072 --> 00:32:41,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What's with her?</font>

537
00:32:42,072 --> 00:32:43,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Dammit!</font>

538
00:33:02,505 --> 00:33:04,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Let's ask these people.</i></font>

539
00:33:04,505 --> 00:33:05,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Merry Christmas.</i></font>

540
00:33:05,805 --> 00:33:07,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-Merry Christmas.
-Merry Christmas.</i></font>

541
00:33:07,705 --> 00:33:10,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>-You're all couples, right?
-Yes.</i></font>

542
00:33:10,405 --> 00:33:14,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>How sweet.
We asked people on the street</i></font>

543
00:33:14,105 --> 00:33:17,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>who they would be spending
Christmas Eve with.</i></font>

544
00:33:17,405 --> 00:33:20,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>The number one answer was,
of course, with a sweetheart.</i></font>

545
00:33:20,672 --> 00:33:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>More than 60 percent gave that answer.</i></font>

546
00:33:27,872 --> 00:33:29,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How pretty.</font>

547
00:34:05,905 --> 00:34:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara...</font>

548
00:34:10,405 --> 00:34:11,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Daichi.</font>

549
00:34:12,072 --> 00:34:16,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I heard your message turning me down,
but you sounded kind of depressed.</font>

550
00:34:16,572 --> 00:34:19,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh, yeah... I'm sorry.</font>

551
00:34:19,939 --> 00:34:21,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Did I cause you trouble?</font>

552
00:34:21,305 --> 00:34:23,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. Come on in.</font>

553
00:34:33,405 --> 00:34:34,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Merry Christmas.</i></font>

554
00:34:34,939 --> 00:34:36,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>How about a delicious,</i></font>

555
00:34:36,105 --> 00:34:38,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-homemade Christmas cake?
-Please be careful with the box.</font>

556
00:34:39,105 --> 00:34:41,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you very much.</font>

557
00:34:42,005 --> 00:34:43,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you very much.</font>

558
00:34:44,405 --> 00:34:47,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Are you sure you want to work?
You had the day off.</font>

559
00:34:47,405 --> 00:34:48,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Of course it's OK.</font>

560
00:34:48,505 --> 00:34:51,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">He wants to spend Christmas Eve
with someone that's special to him.</font>

561
00:34:51,672 --> 00:34:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Isn't that right?</font>

562
00:34:52,972 --> 00:34:54,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who do you mean by "someone special"?</font>

563
00:34:54,505 --> 00:34:55,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh.</font>

564
00:34:55,472 --> 00:34:57,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How about a Christmas cake?</font>

565
00:34:58,072 --> 00:34:59,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>It's very special.</i></font>

566
00:34:59,505 --> 00:35:01,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's a day you spend having fun
and eating cake</font>

567
00:35:01,305 --> 00:35:04,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">with the people who are special to you,
whether it's a sweetheart or family.</font>

568
00:35:05,005 --> 00:35:09,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It can't be just anyone.
It matters who you spend it with.</font>

569
00:35:09,905 --> 00:35:13,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sorry... that I'm not someone special.</font>

570
00:35:17,772 --> 00:35:19,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I can't believe it.</font>

571
00:35:21,039 --> 00:35:22,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thirty-eight point five degrees?</font>

572
00:35:25,605 --> 00:35:28,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How could you not notice?
You can be so dense sometimes.</font>

573
00:35:29,505 --> 00:35:32,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've really been pushing myself lately.</font>

574
00:35:35,839 --> 00:35:38,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Here.
-Thank you.</font>

575
00:35:39,572 --> 00:35:42,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'll make you some porridge,
but is there anything else you'd like?</font>

576
00:35:46,305 --> 00:35:47,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">A cake.</font>

577
00:35:48,072 --> 00:35:50,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can have cake
after you get over this cold.</font>

578
00:35:50,839 --> 00:35:52,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I want to eat a nice, round cake.</font>

579
00:35:54,305 --> 00:35:56,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">The typical strawberry cake</font>

580
00:35:57,405 --> 00:35:59,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that we always had at your house.</font>

581
00:36:00,572 --> 00:36:06,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">We'd all sit around it,
laughing and singing.</font>

582
00:36:10,572 --> 00:36:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you, Daichi.</font>

583
00:36:12,572 --> 00:36:13,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

584
00:36:14,005 --> 00:36:16,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">For spending it with me every year.</font>

585
00:36:20,305 --> 00:36:22,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thanks to you,</font>

586
00:36:22,405 --> 00:36:27,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've never once felt lonely
on Christmas Eve.</font>

587
00:37:13,805 --> 00:37:15,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Thank you.</font>

588
00:37:19,572 --> 00:37:20,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">One cake, please.</font>

589
00:37:20,872 --> 00:37:21,905
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

590
00:37:29,839 --> 00:37:33,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao says she wants to eat one...
like this.</font>

591
00:37:37,672 --> 00:37:39,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That'll be $33.</font>

592
00:37:43,405 --> 00:37:46,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I've always known pretty much everything
that Nao likes.</font>

593
00:37:47,105 --> 00:37:48,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

594
00:37:49,672 --> 00:37:53,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">On Christmas, she likes chicken
and potage soup.</font>

595
00:37:54,005 --> 00:37:57,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She likes that really typical stuff.</font>

596
00:37:58,205 --> 00:37:59,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why are you telling me this?</font>

597
00:38:00,205 --> 00:38:03,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But today, she prepared rolled cabbage
and seafood soup.</font>

598
00:38:05,205 --> 00:38:07,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Even though she's sick,
she went out of her way to make them.</font>

599
00:38:08,072 --> 00:38:10,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What are you trying to tell me?</font>

600
00:38:10,905 --> 00:38:12,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She's not the type to complain.</font>

601
00:38:14,205 --> 00:38:15,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">She never has been.</font>

602
00:38:18,672 --> 00:38:22,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But she's got a fever now,
and said she's lonely.</font>

603
00:38:24,405 --> 00:38:25,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

604
00:38:27,105 --> 00:38:30,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you made her a promise,
then you'd better keep it.</font>

605
00:38:58,039 --> 00:38:59,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>You're the greatest, Daichi.</i></font>

606
00:39:01,305 --> 00:39:02,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Open your eyes.</font>

607
00:39:03,305 --> 00:39:06,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Wow! It's a Hokkori Man sticker.</font>

608
00:39:06,405 --> 00:39:08,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought you'd like it.</font>

609
00:39:08,305 --> 00:39:10,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">How did you know?</font>

610
00:39:11,305 --> 00:39:14,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I just know.
I know everything you like, Nao.</font>

611
00:39:14,872 --> 00:39:18,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the greatest, Daichi!</font>

612
00:39:37,705 --> 00:39:40,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao. I'm coming in.</font>

613
00:40:10,305 --> 00:40:11,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara.</font>

614
00:40:11,872 --> 00:40:13,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Lie back down.</font>

615
00:40:16,305 --> 00:40:17,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What about your work?</font>

616
00:40:18,039 --> 00:40:20,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I took off</font>

617
00:40:20,171 --> 00:40:22,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">after hearing what he had to say.</font>

618
00:40:22,705 --> 00:40:26,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who? Daichi?</font>

619
00:40:27,972 --> 00:40:29,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Nao.</font>

620
00:40:30,305 --> 00:40:31,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes?</font>

621
00:40:35,039 --> 00:40:37,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I know you've got a fever now, but...</font>

622
00:40:41,839 --> 00:40:42,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

623
00:40:47,005 --> 00:40:49,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh... uh...</font>

624
00:40:52,305 --> 00:40:53,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's...</font>

625
00:40:54,572 --> 00:40:57,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">for my job... at the ramen shop.</font>

626
00:40:57,805 --> 00:40:59,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Ramen shop?</font>

627
00:41:02,772 --> 00:41:05,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean you weren't working
at a cafe near the station.</font>

628
00:41:06,205 --> 00:41:07,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No.</font>

629
00:41:08,105 --> 00:41:12,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why did you make up such a stupid thing?</font>

630
00:41:12,405 --> 00:41:14,939
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-I couldn't help it.
-Why?</font>

631
00:41:15,672 --> 00:41:19,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Sometimes you don't want people
to see you looking a certain way.</font>

632
00:41:20,039 --> 00:41:21,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

633
00:41:22,939 --> 00:41:25,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">If you saw me delivering ramen
when I was dressed like this,</font>

634
00:41:25,405 --> 00:41:27,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">you'd make fun of me.</font>

635
00:41:30,405 --> 00:41:34,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yeah, it is pretty awful looking.</font>

636
00:41:36,705 --> 00:41:41,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That outfit...
isn't anything to brag about either.</font>

637
00:41:41,305 --> 00:41:42,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

638
00:41:49,105 --> 00:41:50,805
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Stop laughing.</font>

639
00:41:54,939 --> 00:41:58,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're the only one
that I didn't want to see me like that.</font>

640
00:41:59,205 --> 00:42:00,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Why?</font>

641
00:42:03,005 --> 00:42:06,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I mean, we see each other every day.</font>

642
00:42:08,305 --> 00:42:10,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm adding one more rule to the list.</font>

643
00:42:11,405 --> 00:42:12,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

644
00:42:12,839 --> 00:42:16,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Don't put on an act.
Lean on others when you need to.</font>

645
00:42:18,972 --> 00:42:22,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I could have helped you
and prevented you from getting sick.</font>

646
00:42:25,505 --> 00:42:28,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Who was it that collapsed the other day?</font>

647
00:42:28,105 --> 00:42:30,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's not important.
Are you going to follow the rules?</font>

648
00:42:31,605 --> 00:42:33,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Yes.</font>

649
00:42:36,705 --> 00:42:37,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

650
00:42:38,605 --> 00:42:40,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">-Is that a cake?
-Yeah.</font>

651
00:42:40,772 --> 00:42:43,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">That's great. Can I look?</font>

652
00:42:44,039 --> 00:42:46,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But no eating until your fever goes down.</font>

653
00:42:46,205 --> 00:42:47,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">OK.</font>

654
00:42:50,605 --> 00:42:51,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uh-oh.</font>

655
00:42:53,405 --> 00:42:55,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Crap. I shouldn't have run.</font>

656
00:43:02,072 --> 00:43:02,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey! Don't!</font>

657
00:43:03,705 --> 00:43:05,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I said no eating.</font>

658
00:43:08,205 --> 00:43:10,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">See. I bet you're feeling sick now,
aren't you?</font>

659
00:43:11,905 --> 00:43:14,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">No. It's delicious.</font>

660
00:43:16,305 --> 00:43:18,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But if he made you his girlfriend</font>

661
00:43:18,405 --> 00:43:21,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">that's exactly why he'd treat you
with very special care.</font>

662
00:43:24,205 --> 00:43:26,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm fine with the way things are now.</font>

663
00:43:27,105 --> 00:43:28,205
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

664
00:43:29,205 --> 00:43:32,405
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm fine just like this.</font>

665
00:43:32,505 --> 00:43:35,839
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You can't stay like that.
Your fever's still super high.</font>

666
00:43:37,505 --> 00:43:38,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You're right.</font>

667
00:43:54,105 --> 00:43:56,005
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I'm going to have a taste of this.</font>

668
00:43:59,572 --> 00:44:00,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey!</font>

669
00:44:19,305 --> 00:44:22,305
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Hey, Nao. I got some milk pudding.</font>

670
00:44:34,205 --> 00:44:37,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>I'm feeling better,
so I'm going for a walk in the park.</i></font>

671
00:44:37,605 --> 00:44:38,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71"><i>Nao.</i></font>

672
00:44:39,205 --> 00:44:40,171
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What?</font>

673
00:44:48,205 --> 00:44:50,972
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">What did you want to see me for, Nao?</font>

674
00:44:51,205 --> 00:44:54,572
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I thought I should tell you the truth,
Abe.</font>

675
00:44:55,205 --> 00:44:58,472
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">You mean, you want to date me?</font>

676
00:45:00,605 --> 00:45:06,505
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">It's just like you said.
Uehara and I aren't dating.</font>

677
00:45:06,605 --> 00:45:07,672
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Really?</font>

678
00:45:08,039 --> 00:45:12,872
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Uehara doesn't have any feelings for me.</font>

679
00:45:12,939 --> 00:45:14,039
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Then, you mean...</font>

680
00:45:14,672 --> 00:45:15,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">But...</font>

681
00:45:18,972 --> 00:45:21,605
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like Uehara.</font>

682
00:45:22,905 --> 00:45:23,772
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Huh?</font>

683
00:45:29,972 --> 00:45:35,105
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">I like... Uehara.</font>

684
00:45:46,605 --> 00:45:48,072
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">Oh!</font>

685
00:47:27,505 --> 00:47:29,705
<font face="sans-serif" size="71">THIS IS A FICTIONAL DRAMA.</font>
